📘 Legal Calculus 4.5
Tier 7 — Procedural Memory & Public Archive
Module 91 – Education Pack: Teach Once, Scale Forever 🎒📦
⚖️ Core Message
A clean teaching pack (slides + handouts + assignments + answer keys) turns your case into a course others can teach without you.

📖 Lesson Content
• Slides — 10‑slide deck: problem, record, doctrine, tools, impact.
• Handouts — Two modules + Top‑10 + verification guide.
• Assignments — Verify three exhibits; draft Paper Hearing Q&A.
• Keys — Short answers; model filings.
• License — Open license; attribution note; contact for updates.
📝 Assignment
Publish an 'Education Pack' folder with a slide deck PDF, two module handouts, assignments, and keys.

✅ Model Answer (Template)
SLIDE TITLES: Filing is Protest; Evidence Lives in the Record; Paper Hearing; Chain‑Verified Citations; Tools Appendix.

💡 Reflection
When others can teach it, the idea spreads without you in the room.

🎨 Visual Pairing
A backpack icon with a mini slide deck and handout sheets.



